{"tid":1019095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【東森TVBS斷章取義】 支持罷工變反罷工 受訪者出鏡大控訴","createTime":"2019-02-12T16:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T02:57:46.000Z","uid":117200,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c29eff94a69d2815a3f61cec7af24079b3d5a5ab","tid":1019095,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/51708383_2299737306717065_2597431925236826112_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=2e8ea5b9dd40c2f34ed19f55b692ef58&amp;oe=5CDFA7D4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F51708383_2299737306717065_2597431925236826112_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D2e8ea5b9dd40c2f34ed19f55b692ef58%26oe%3D5CDFA7D4&h=dcd7edfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【新聞斷章取義vs受訪者真實說法】 <br />\n<br />\nAda Chu：<br />\n請看兩隻影片的差異！<br />\n我說了兩次「班機延誤對我工作影響不大。」<br />\n又說「我並不追究損失補償， 因為我支持罷工行動。」<br />\n還說「我請個假很ok，因為我支持勞權意識提升。」<br />\n東森把我整段支持罷工行動的言論剪掉，只剪出我如實解釋的候補情況，並刻意剪出我說「現在班機沒位子」。<br />\n<br />\n而我背後的標題下的是「客怨傻等」、「客怨賠償」。<br />\n我從頭到尾說我不需要賠償，沒抱怨等待候位，也說班機延誤的影響在我可接受範圍。<br />\n而&ldquo;TVBS似乎是沒放我的畫面&rdquo;（但也可能是找不到）<br />\n<br />\n怎麼會這樣😅<br />\n補：為了讓我的說法更有說服力，證明我不是空口說白話，我放了第二個影片，是東森訪問的側錄，我剪輯了自己的真實說法！<br />\n<br />\n歡迎分享！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tzuyi.chu.56/videos/2327074913969798/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftzuyi.chu.56%2Fvideos%2F2327074913969798%2F&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwidnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=ff0e5254\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tzuyi.chu.56/videos/2327074913969798/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tzuyi.chu.56/videos/2327384767272146/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftzuyi.chu.56%2Fvideos%2F2327384767272146%2F&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwidnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=c446ee1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tzuyi.chu.56/videos/2327384767272146/</a>"},{"pid":"13f52aa68fbe11f65a1dc61c2c53def706d66d3c","tid":1019095,"uid":17646,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"仲以為東森新聞好少少<br />\n原來係cctvb朋友"},{"pid":"131078980c61b9297b191adffc2f7b0cdf513495","tid":1019095,"uid":11556,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:22:30.000Z","msg":"東森藍到不得了架<br />\n呀唔係，依家應該係紅到不得了。<br />\n<br />\n東森，TVBS，中天 紅底三兄弟"},{"pid":"1c94fa3f4d23d830e39a6cb7214e9c25617e4c40","tid":1019095,"uid":196099,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:44:45.000Z","msg":"台灣垃圾媒體一覽<br />\n中天 中視 東森 tvbs 聯合 中視<br />\n清流<br />\n公廣集團旗下 公視 華視<br />\n明顯意識形態但尚可觀看<br />\n三立 民視"},{"pid":"8f482fd589f281bf3dd83056618da9d3095232be","tid":1019095,"uid":190333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c94fa3f4d23d830e39a6cb7214e9c25617e4c40","tid":1019095,"uid":196099,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:44:45.000Z","msg":"台灣垃圾媒體一覽<br />\n中天 中視 東森 tvbs 聯合 中視<br />\n清流<br />\n公廣集團旗下 公視 華視<br />\n明顯意識形態但尚可觀看<br />\n三立 民視"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:50:33.000Z","msg":"三立同民視一樣畀人話幫住DPP同空心菜<br />\n最緊要case by case獨立思考<br />\n公視就多數反對工程基建"},{"pid":"88ecbd9cdd095f881cfd605eda506bdcf3d1c26a","tid":1019095,"uid":109102,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:58:03.000Z","msg":"睇關鍵時刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf33889ed16dc5e14781da4c852abd58052cb72f","tid":1019095,"uid":190333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88ecbd9cdd095f881cfd605eda506bdcf3d1c26a","tid":1019095,"uid":109102,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:58:03.000Z","msg":"睇關鍵時刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T18:02:29.000Z","msg":"寶傑"},{"pid":"ade8b80b2f98f1beb5cd0fba177796c9e4f5d569","tid":1019095,"uid":52946,"like":6